 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Associate General Counsel, Insurance Lemonade Insurance Company 2 reviews SoHo, NY Full-time Lemonade Insurance Company 2 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Full-time Full Job Description Soho, New York | Legal/Compliance | Full-time 
 
We are seeking a motivated and adaptable insurance regulatory lawyer to extend our legal, compliance, and regulatory infrastructure. Our ideal candidate is able to synthesize a broad range of legal skills and P&C industry knowledge and apply the results to a broad range of legal issues, all within a hyper-growth startup environment. 
 
In this role, you will be provide guidance regarding insurance-related laws and regulations, policy interpretations, claims handling, agency relationships, reinsurance, financial condition, statutory filings, marketing, and other issues. You’ll partner with Compliance, Finance and other teams to develop policies and procedures, and respond to regulatory inquiries, including financial and market conduct exams. You will also support our government relations and enterprise risk management functions. 
 
Requirements 
5+ years experience in a Big Law corporate practice within the insurance field, and/or in-house corporate experience with an insurance company 
5+ years property/casualty experience 
Superior research, writing, communication, and drafting skills 
Bar admission in good standing (New York preferred) 
Bachelor’s degree in Finance, Economics, or Accounting (MBA is a plus) 
You’re a problem solver who is curious, skeptical, analytical, creative, and detail-oriented 
About Lemonade 
Lemonade is a licensed insurance carrier offering renters, homeowners, life, and pet insurance in the United States, contents and liability insurance in Germany and the Netherlands, and renters insurance in France. We’re powered by artificial intelligence and behavioral economics, and driven by social good. 
A Certified B-Corp, Lemonade donates unused premiums to nonprofits selected by its community as part of our annual Giveback program. We incorporate our values into everything we do—from our business model to our office culture. Lemonade Insurance Company 2 days ago original job Report job You must create an Indeed account before continuing to the company website to apply Apply Now Apply On Company Site Save this job Save this job Associate General Counsel jobs in SoHo, NY Jobs at Lemonade Insurance Company in SoHo, NY Associate General Counsel salaries in SoHo, NY Company Info Follow Get job updates from Lemonade Insurance Company 2 reviews Let employers find you Thousands of employers search for candidates on Indeed Upload your resume 
 
